_aChangeLog.text: changed terrain surface for T spawn for a better experience
removed trucks from CT spawn and added a raildroad with a train and wagons
added lockers on A site - entry
removed some stones in T spawn, where bots were stuck
added lights in A site at windows for a better visibility
removed overlay decal (saying Romania flag) that was placed on the rocket on B site, Pakrat Error, i changed it with simple texture
changed some models with blocktools and converted to func_detail
added a corridor to bombsite A for more spots
added nav_edit to bots to use ladders
deleted a tree that causes low fps on some spots
changed T spwn thanks to user Frikadellendieb
